text: KXIM (98.3 FM) is a radio station licensed to serve the community of Sanborn, Iowa. The station is owned by AM-770 Radio Engineering, and airs a variety format. The station was assigned the KXIM call letters by the Federal Communications Commission on August 14, 2012. ==References== ==External links== * Official Website * XIM Category:Radio stations established in 2015 Category:2015 establishments in Iowa Category:Variety radio stations in the United States Category:O'Brien County, Iowa
